      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Confirm that failed material cannot be reworked and determine if a waiver is required. Generate a request for waiver on failed material and circulate to appropriate approval parties (i.e.production operations, customers, etc.). A request for waiver is a request to use material that has failed an inspection or quality requirement.&#10;"/>
